import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-fetch-tatwas', templateUrl: './fetch-tatwas.component.html' }) export class FetchTatwasComponent { public tatwas: Tatwa[] = []; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + 'tatwa').subscribe(result => { this.tatwas = result; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface Tatwa { name: string; element: string; attributes: string; rulingplanets: string; duration: string; dayswhenfirst: string[]; }
